org.jetel.plugin

Class PluginLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.plugin.PluginLocation

  • public class PluginLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represent a location of a clover engine plugin. Internally is implemented by a URL of plugin repository and optional class loader which should be used as default class loader of all plugins placed in the repository.
